# The real per-language API docs are generated into static/sdk/<lang>/ by the
# coupled docs build and deployed, never committed — only the placeholder
# index.html files are tracked. Ignoring the *contents* (not the dirs) lets the
# index.html negation take effect.
/static/sdk/*/*
!/static/sdk/*/index.html
